description:
Skating on Thin Ice is an anti-drug public service announcement that takes place in Canada. Peter Parker Convinces J. Jonah Jameson to go to Winnipeg to do some investigating after a brief run through with Electro. Spider-Man Follows Electro to Canada on a major drug bust, all the while, Spider-man is teaching some kids to make the right choices along with hockey legend Herb Conegie (African-American hockey legend) making a guest appearance.

There is a Canadian logo - version with a bigger number and Canadian prize: $ 1.25 CAN.
See cover below.
name: Skating on Thin Ice!

description:
Cathy Grant, the intrepid young peace corps volunteer from The Temporary Natives, discovers a terrifying lesson in the history of her Central African post; of a country imprisoned in a madman's grip; of a dictator who pitted brother against brother, and who caused the deaths of hundreds in the name of power. And, against this tale is hung a greater story of survival, hope and love.

Color, Prestige Format, 48 pages.
name: A Tale From The Heart Of Africa

volume.name: Bloodlines: A Tale From The Heart Of Africa

The Cenobites are back in this adaptation of the third Hellraiser feature film! Pinhead rebels against his god, Leviathan, and focuses his attention on Earth--to make it his personal Hell!

description: It's 1945, and World War II is almost over - but Hydra founder Baron Wolfgang von Strucker is already planning the next one with insider information from the future! It's up to the Invaders to re-write Strucker's history books and drive down his Dragon of Death! Then, more than ten years later, Doctor Druid forms the Monster Hunters to face another pivotal enemy, one whose schemes date back centuries! Collecting MARVEL UNIVERSE #1-7.
name: Invaders: Eve of Destruction

description: On a tropical island in the Atlantic Ocean in the mid-seventeenth century, a village awakens in terror, invaded by a band of conquistadors. When it's over, there will be no survivors among the inhabitants. Men, women, children, have all been killed and burned. Why? There seems to be no motive.  There's no raping, pillaging or theft of any kind. Hutatsu and Dathcino, two native Indians who are neighbors to the village happen upon the scene.  They don't ask questions about the motives, rather they look on it as a godsend and opportunity for eat and drink their fill, while appropriating items the dead left behind...until they are discovered.
name: Santa Maladria

description: The beginning of the end? They are the greatest heroes the world has ever known: Captain America, Iron Man, Thor, Hulk, Wasp, Giant Man, Hawkeye, Black Widow, Quicksilver, Scarlet Witch. They've saved the world from alien invasion, becoming international celebrities and America's champions, but now all that's about to change. Can the Ultimates survive the Hulk's execution, Thor's imprisonment, and the advent of the Ultimate Defenders?! On the eve of Tony and Natasha's wedding, Nick Fury makes his move against the mysterious traitor that's been plaguing the team - and the Ultimates will never be the same! The world's greatest heroes are in for the battle of the century, and not all of them will be walking away. Collecting ULTIMATES 2 #1-13 and ULTIMATES 2 #1 VARIANT SKETCH EDITION.
name: Ultimates 2 Ultimate Collection

description: Avatar's troubles abound as a hated enemy returns from the past to torment the immortal Futurian. Avater flashes back to the time of King Arthur when he was known as Merlin the Magician to relive the events that birthed his most bitter foe. It's a fantasy masterpiece that just had to be called 'One Grief Shining Moment.' Cover by Michael Netzer.
name: One Grief Shining Moment.

description:
English title translation:  Waiting for Death  

The Conquistadors and Indians are waging a bloody war. A terrible disease afflicts both sides, and the fate of this small world of fire and blood is now in the hands of two teenagers and a young girl! They become separated -  Dathcino, the young thief falls into the clutches of the Captain of the Conquistadors, and discovers first hand the horror of the camps where humans are used for experimentation. His accomplice, Hutatsu wanders the island in search of a strategy to save his friend. Meanwhile, the young Initsiii is doing everything possible to help those afflicted with the dreadful disease...
name: Esperar la muerte

description: In this sequel to THE FLASH: DEAD HEAT, the Flash finds himself lost in time after defeating the evil Savitar. Trapped in the 64 century, the Scarlet Speedster encounters inconceivable horrors in a future he could never have imagined. Hoping to use the love that he shares with his girlfriend as a beacon, Flash tries to find his way back to his own era. Unfortunately, a new speedster named John Fox, who is trying to usurp his identity and steal his girlfriend, has convinced Linda that he is dead. Now Flash must overcome the complexities of time and the machinations of a new enemy in order to reclaim his life.
name: The Flash: Race Against Time

description:
English translation of title:  Everybody's sick! 
 
The entire island is now ravaged by the disease. No one, including the three friends the story centers around have escaped. Initsii, the Syyanas princess is very ill, and her father is trying everything, including the sacrifice of newborns, to save her. Hutatsu, who has fallen into the hands of the conquistadors will tell them about betrayal of Abatirso. Meanwhile, Dathcino is serving as a guinea pig for doctors trying in vain to stem the spread of the disease. Three fates are intertwined in a struggle against invaders, the disease and the struggle for dignity and freedom.
name: Todos enfermos!

description:
sakura is a Japanese schoolgirl who has taken to Street Fighting. Inspired by a battle that she witnessed, she now strives to follow the example of a man whose name she does not know.

Her talent as a fighter has attracted the attention of Dan, a martial artist who despite his overinflated sense of his own prowess as a warrior, provides Sakura with fairly solid guidance.

Sakura's quest begins at home, as her success in street brawls draws the eye of her classmate Karin Kanzuki, the heir of a powerful conglomerate and a consummate martial artist herself. Following their bout, Karin hosts a fighting tournament in Sakura's hometown, drawing in martial artists from around the world, including one who could bring Sakura far closer to finding the warrior who inspired her.
name: Setagaya-ku Sakura

description: Sakura's quest goes international as she and Dan travel the world in order to find Ryu and allow Sakura to better herself as a martial artist. Along the way they encounter many familiar faces before finding what they seek.
name: Until I Meet That Person I Saw

description: Fox Features Syndicate presents the one and only appearance of Count Rorret "The Black Tarantula!" A strange pseudo-vampire who wreaks havoc in the kingdom of Minnerville! And only Princess Elthena and the Brave Leopold can stop him!
name: A Feature Presentation..The Black Tarantula

description: Fox Feature Syndicate presents it's Adaptation of Herman Mellville's "Moby Dick".
name: A Feature Presentation...Moby Dick

description: Zeke O'Brien may have his eyes on the title of Black Knight--the highest honor that can be bestowed upon a knight in the kingdom of Aran--but he's also after another prize: The young prince, Chris!
name: Vol. 1

description: The shadow of the Dundalk Empire once again looms over the Kingdom of Aran. Zeke O'Brien, a knight under his lover’s command must protect the beloved third Prince Christen Wilson Jeremy Cronmacnoise. Zeke is teaching Christen about swordsmanship, honor and love. The plot thickens as Chris garners the courage to ask his father to allow him to represent Kingdom of Aran in battle! The King and Zeke both disapprove, but will their disapproval be enough to stop a man that loves his kingdom more than his own life?
name: Vol. 2

description: Eager to prove his worth to his kingdom, Prince Christian has taken cover in Brigadoon's caravan as a hostage to infiltrate the Dundalk Empire. Negotions for peace between the kingdoms is all the young prince yearns for, but the rebellious Falcon's Talon group has something else in mind... Now Zeke's loyalty as Christian's knight and lover will be put to the test in this heroic quest for justice.
name: Vol. 3

description: Chris, the third prince of the Kingdom of Aran, and Zeke, his knight in shining armor, have always been there for each other. But these two lovers must hide their forbidden romance as political intrigue and conspiracy swirl around them. Will Zeke be able to rescue his captured lord before it's too late?!
name: Vol. 4

description: Sachunsa returns to the island to find that although he has obtained the crystal containing the heat energy of the Human Face Fire Dragon, it is impossible for the Commander of the Continental Alliance Military to eat it. This is due to the strict law of Snail Province--the law of utter submission to the Thief King! Thus begins Sachunsa's one-man rebellion against all that Snail Province stands for...
name: Vol. 9

description: In this next volume of Blade of Heaven, at the start of the Hero Competition, the underhanded, devious plot of the Demon Majeh has been put into effect!
name: Vol. 10

description:
Cibo's body dies in the battle between the Electrofishers and the Safeguard. Killy siphons power from a dead Exterminator to unlock the limiter on his Graviton Beam Emitter. He destroys the Great Cyst Safeguard and most of the surrounding area. Killy and Cibo, transplanted into Sana-kan's body are the only living beings. Cibo believes information about Net Terminal Genes are in a correctly-functioning AI somewhere close.

Back Blurb

When Cibo's body dies during the battle between the Electrofishers and the Safeguard, her consciousness is teleported to a Backup Cyberspace, where she overloads the program the Safeguard is using to control its troops. But this won't stave off the troops for long. And unless Killy figures out a way to unlock the limiter on his Gravitor Beam Emitter, the guest for the Net Terminal Genes might come to a crashing end!

Chapter Titles

  • LOG - 19: Backup Cyberspace
  • LOG - 20: Limiter Release
  • LOG - 21: Hybrid
  • LOG - 22: Toha Heavy Industries
  • LOG - 23: Electroknight
  • LOG - 24: The Eight Cave
name: Vol. 4

description:
Killy has been blazing through the deadly caves of Toha Heavy Industries. But even as he comes closer to finding humans with Net Terminal Genes, the one thing he's been trying to avoid stands in his way...

Chapter Titles

  • LOG - 25: Hacking
  • LOG - 26: Scattered Caves
  • LOG - 27: Gravity Furnace
  • LOG - 28: Version
  • LOG - 29: The Thirteenth Cave
  • LOG - 30: Ceasefire
name: Vol. 5

description:
Killy is blazing guns in this sixth installation of Blame! Killy and Cibo must find the Net Terminal Genes to save what's left of the human race. In the alternate dimension will Killy be able to solve the mystery behind the Silicon Creatures.

Back Blurb

Multiple showdowns hit simultaneously in the cyberdungeon world of BLAME... and Killy is just one Graviton Beam Emitter away from meeting his ultimate maker.

Chapter Titles

  • LOG - 31: Sana-kan and Cibo
  • LOG - 32: Vibration
  • LOG - 33: Breakdown
  • LOG - 34: Meltdown
  • LOG - 35: Obliteration
  • LOG - 36: Beautiful Life
  • LOG - 37: Unofficial Megastructure
name: Vol. 6

description:
Dhomochevsky and his ghostly companion Ico are unusual Safeguards: they are programmed to protect all the humans on their floor, not just those with pure Net Terminal Genes. But will they be able to protect Killy and Cibo from the Silicon Creatures who have infiltrated their level...and who seek a human genetic sample just like the one Cibo has obtained?

Chapter Titles

  • LOG - 38: The Repository
  • LOG - 39: Type 1 Critical Contingent Weapon
  • LOG - 40: Seizure
  • LOG - 41: Electron Space Barrier
  • LOG - 42: Megastructure Internal Rupture
  • LOG - 43: Temporary Safeguards
name: Vol. 7

description:
Killy and Dhomochevsky don't trust each other, but they have a more pressing concern: retrieving Cibo's capsule of human genetic information. The capsule has been stolen by the Silicon Creatures, who will use it to attempt a provisional connection to the Netsphere. Can our unlikely allies stop them in time, or is it already too late?

Chapter Titles

  • LOG - 45: Molecular Dispersion
  • LOG - 46: Provisional Connection Certification
  • LOG - 47: Penetration
  • LOG - 48: Impulse
  • LOG - 49: Level 9
  • LOG - 50: Distance
name: Vol. 8

description: In the aftermath of an apocalyptic battle, Killy is on the brink of death. Cibo fusion with the Level 9 Safeguard unit has reduced her once-impressive intellect to that of a child. Can a now child-like Cibo find Killy while avoiding the merciless Silicon Creatures?
name: Vol. 9

description: Killy's journey takes him back to where it all began for him. The man of few words that he is, he saves the central city by granting it its greatest wish...the elimination of the silicate creatures. But there is much much more to the mystery... And will saving the city cost him his life and end his search for Net Terminal Genes?
name: Vol. 10

description:
Follow the misadventures of Blank, a screwed-up secret agent with a serious lapse in memory, and Aki, the confused tomboy whom he has sworn to protect, as they go deep undercover in that most dangerous of territories--high school! Between cramming for classes, mixing it up with the school thugs, and uncovering a dark plot laid by the terrorist organization Raizen, the two may just fall in love--if they don't kill each other first!

---------------

Murder, deceit, dames... and trig tests?

The life of a secret agent is not an easy one, especially when you have amnesia. So when the thick-witted young pervert who calls himself Blank shows up at her school claiming to be one, Aki Clark has every reason to be skeptical. However, between his dedication, his ridiculous way with women, and his ability to make her laugh, Aki finds herself drawn to this man with no memory. But when they find themselves in the midst of a dark plot by the terrorist organization Raizen, Blank had better remember his secret agent skills quickly, or risk losing a lot more than his memory.

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 1: Weirdos and Perverts andFreaks, OH MY!
  • Chapter 2: The Trouble With Blank
  • Chapter 3: The Calm Before the Storm
  • Chapter 4: Girl Trouble
  • Chapter 5: New Day Raizan
  • Chapter 6: Bringin' Down da' House
name: Vol. 1

description: Sting, Major Fleetwood, and Leanne McDuff head toward Sub-Texas to face the last person on Fleetwood's list: the vicious Jim Bowie. On their mission, they befriend Red Cloud, the young chief of the Tribal League that is also searching for Bowie. But with two groups targeting him, Jim Bowie may have something up his sleeve to surprise his attackers!
name: Vol. 9

description: Sting may look harmless, but looks can be deceiving... Join the young bounty hunter as he fights his way across a futuristic wild west. Get ready for all-out war! As his scouts are massacred, Blue Cloud decides to abandon the fort and launch a surprise attack on Jim Bowie's troops. Sting, Leanne McDuff and Major Fleetwood participate in their advancement to attack, but they're served a special dollop of trouble when Bowie's personal goons, the Scorpions, appear!
name: Vol. 10

description: Nurse Yuki Akabane is a descendant of a line of vampires. He's often visited at the hospital he works at by a donor nut named Osamu Mayuzumi, the insatiable cram school teacher. Yuki never really thought twice about Mayuzumi, but when he drinks some of his blood on a whim, it tastes so good to him that he tries to get closer to him to savor more. But what will he do when Mayuzumi suddenly stops coming...?!
name: Vol. 1

description:
With the help of his right hand man Kuraha, Migiri has been brought back to life and granted a sacrifice in the form of the beautiful young Kikuri. The only thing standing in the way of Migiri's restoration is Yusuke Himukai, who is sworn to protect Kikuri!

Chapter Titles

  • Prologue - Samurai Chronicle
  • Chapter 1 - Soiled Fangs 1
  • Chapter 2 - Soiled Fangs 2
  • Chapter 3 - Soiled Fangs 3
  • Chapter 4 - Soiled Fangs 4
  • Chapter 5 - Soiled Fangs 5
name: Vol. 1

description: Hiiragi--Hikage's sister--is sent to do a dangerous job; she partners with a group of assassins to go after Kazuma. But Kazuma is a worthier adversary than everyone had thought! When Hikage learns of the group's hit job, he rushed off with Yusuke to save his sister. But will he be able to make it in time--and even if he does, do they even stand a chance against Kazuma?
name: Vol. 2

description: Blood is spilled in this tale of darkness and intrigue. Kazuma patiently waits for our heroes to make their way to him. Yusuke and Hideko are still being hunted by the vicious Migiri. Migiri's choir of demons and beautiful priestess are slowly spreading his evil doctrine. Can Yusuke assist Hideko and stop Migiri at the same time?
name: Vol. 3
